{"tid":2398512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發 商場免疫！","createTime":"2021-02-07T11:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T14:17:50.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"747b9c12b2405da8fb1519cb415f3294047a8952","tid":2398512,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"　　​政府今日（二月七日）引用《預防及控制疾病（對若干人士強制檢測）規例》（第599J章），作出限制與檢測宣告（下稱「相關宣告」），自下午七時起限制在旺角指明「受限區域」（即旺角海庭道2號海富苑海裕閣（<span class=\"red\">不包括海富商場</span>），見附件）內的人士（下稱受檢人士）須留在其處所並接受強制檢測。受檢人士須在其處所等候，直至區內所有已識別的受檢人士完成檢測，而相關檢測結果亦已獲大致確定，方可離開其處所。政府目標是在明日（二月八日）上午約七時左右完成此行動，以達致「同心抗疫，小區『清零』」的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff2f7d694f944898e4f6e7f33c6f7e5e9666ae1","tid":2398512,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"以為 金鐘果個"},{"pid":"20b0da3566004e971a91189382dce57a79fb6dd4","tid":2398512,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"港共又同武肺病毒傾好咗數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9eb681df5bce14e75e860bc3afb40f388398b5b","tid":2398512,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"海富前幾日有確診咩?<br />\n無確診點解又封個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935107c740a6ed3f6290768b8d17277bf8b3a08f","tid":2398512,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"太古城都好多人排隊食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86209052dd5130244905a19174245888281f7a71","tid":2398512,"uid":117509,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"咁樣抗疫<img src=\